<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jamir - Resume</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .resume-container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .profile-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .profile-image {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 3px solid #4a6fa5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 2.2em;
        }
        .title {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #3498db;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        .education-item, .contact-item {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .education-item h3, .contact-item h3 {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .education-item p, .contact-item p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        .introduction {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #34495e;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .resume-container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="resume-container">
        <header class="profile-header">
            <img src="jam.png" alt="Professional headshot of John Doe wearing business casual attire in front of a blurred office background" class="profile-image">
            <h1>Jamir Kurt Quillang</h1>
            <p class="title">BSIT-AIT 1-2</p>
        </header>

        <section class="introduction">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>
                I'm Jamir Kurt Quillang and I'm 20 years old. I live in Taguig City, Philippines. Since I'm in Senior High School being an Software Engineer is always my dream. I love coding as well as debugging. Since, I'm a tech guy being in love in coding makes me calm. I'm a former National University - Manila student and transferred to Philsca, since Philsca is my dream school ever since.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="education">
            <h2>Education</h2>
            <div class="education-item">
                <h3>STI College - Global City</h3>
                <p>Senior High School, 2021-2023</p>
            </div>
            <div class="education-item">
                <h3>Undergrad Bachelor of Science in Information Technology</h3>
                <p>National University - Manila, 2023-2025</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="contact">
            <h2>Contact Information</h2>
            <div class="contact-item">
                <h3>Email</h3>
                <p>kuajheko@gmail.com</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-item">
                <h3>Phone</h3>
                <p>09930681280</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-item">
                <h3>GitHub</h3>
                <p>https://github.com/celestiaagatha</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

